{"type": "article", "id": 17371, "title": "Jean Nouvel 设计的音响", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-11T06:34:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000358eBaxnrc8mD1s9SR3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是法国建筑师 Jean Nouvel 为他备受争议的巴黎音乐厅设计的音响，再由法国专业厂商艾玛迪斯（Amadeus）修改生产。它有 1.6 米高，上面的音响部分由 547 层薄型胶合板叠成，经过加工后形成弯曲的结构，有点像船的甲板，其实有助于排除外界低频率的声音干扰，令音色饱满。 而这种叠加也让木纹显得很自然。<a href=\"http://philharmoniabyjeannouvel.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144444osV6DYS50XPpyQTH.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.85574572\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144445nqJWxr7fk1w0Ilti.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1089\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33129584\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144445pyzmxG7VwP6A8Odl.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1089\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33129584\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144446S9PuJTn7bENXoF8L.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1227\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144447TmJRbaQAu79pOgPr.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}